                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="12560309" author="sauthieg" created="Fri, 18 Jan 2008 09:00:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;As a side note, I can add that ContentClassLoader.findResource(String) (the one that return only 1 URL, not an enumeration) only look for local content, even if the bundle&apos;s state is RESOLVED.&lt;br/&gt;
I guess it should use the ISearchPolicy too?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12560357" author="sauthieg" created="Fri, 18 Jan 2008 12:18:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This super easy patch only delegate the ContentClassLoader finResource*() methods to the module&apos;s ISearchPolicy.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12562558" author="rickhall" created="Fri, 25 Jan 2008 16:28:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I committed this patch, I think the issue can be closed now.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
